{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Modified version of X-Raym's "X-Raym_Add point on envelopes at edit cursor.lua"; instead of just adding a point for the momentary value along the existing envelope curve, this script adds a point for the current value of the parameter. The use case is latch-preview mode, if the user makes a change she likes and wants to print it as a point to the automation lane at the time under the edit cursor.\par}
}

