{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Inspired by {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://youtu.be/HEVKLiWkRkk"}}{\fldrslt{\ul
Kenny Gioia's "Razor Edit - Fast Mode in REAPER"
}}}
, this script makes the appropriate changes to the Mouse Modifier preferences to support fast Razor Editing. Improved over what Kenny can do using standard actions is that the shift-modified left-drag actions are incorporated with the "ignoring snap" action variants.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The workflow is also simpler, as it's just a single toggle script. It can be hooked up to a key command and/or a toolbar button. For best results add as a global startup action to initialize the toggle state\par}
}

